name: Genesis
description: Genesis (GXN) powers the Genesis Incubations ecosystem, an AI-enhanced Web3 incubator transforming token launches through automation, security, and transparency. Built on Ethereum, GXN fuels project funding, governance, and utility access across Genesis and its partner platform SparkStarter. Leveraging AI analytics, smart contract auditing, and a 30-day vault system, Genesis ensures compliant, data-driven project growth. GXN is the key to a next-generation launchpad network bridging innovation, accountability, and real-world blockchain utility.
